data.description: SELLER OFFERING $10K in concessions with FULL price offer! Buyer can use for 2/1 rate buydown or closing costs, whatever they want!  We are thrilled to present to you this stunning single-level living ranch, nestled within the coveted Jefferson City School Cluster! This beautiful home is a true gem, boasting an array of features that will undoubtedly capture your heart. As you step through the front door, your eyes will be immediately drawn to the exquisite cathedral ceilings, creating a sense of grandeur and spaciousness. The open floor plan seamlessly integrates the spacious kitchen, complete with a large island and seating, granite countertops, custom tile backsplash, under-head lighting, and stainless steel appliances. The view from the kitchen to the family room makes this home a perfect space for entertaining friends and family. Additionally, you'll find a separate space just off the family room, which can be transformed into your dream office or an elegant dining area. With 4 bedrooms & 2.5 baths, this home is ideal for a growing family. The oversized master bedroom is adorned with trey ceilings, adding a touch of grandeur to your private sanctuary. The master ensuite is a haven of relaxation, featuring a double vanity, a separate shower, a soothing soaking tub, and a generously sized walk-in closet. Step outside, and you'll discover a large, flat, fenced-in lot with a cozy covered deck equipped with fans—perfect for dining al fresco and hosting summer BBQs. What's more, the home backs up to quiet woods filled with trails, offering opportunities for outdoor adventures and 4-wheeling right in your own backyard. The location of this property is truly exceptional, as it's only 8 minutes away from Downtown Jefferson shopping & restaurants galore and, of course, situated within the highly sought-after Jefferson City School Cluster. The combination of this price and location is simply unbeatable, making this home a "must-see" in every sense of the word. Don't delay, as homes of this caliber do not stay on the market for long! Schedule your showing TODAY!!
